## Read Order (Mandatory)

```
1. APP.md              ← Understand what this is (identity, purpose, scope)
2. CLAUDE.md           ← Understand how to code for it (rules, patterns)
3. docs/GUARDRAILS.md  ← Understand what NOT to do (hard limits)
4. docs/KNOWLEDGE.md   ← Find existing resources before building new
5. docs/DECISIONS.md   ← Don't re-open settled decisions
6. docs/WORKFLOWS.md   ← Follow established patterns
7. docs/ARCHITECTURE.md ← Understand system structure (when making changes)
8. docs/ROADMAP.md     ← Know current priorities (when picking tasks)
```

